*Levo* me je zgužvano zglobno prstenje (My left knuckle ring was bent)

*Levom* rukom sam zgrabio njegovu torbu (I grabbed his bag with my left hand)

*Levo* krilo je udario u zid (The left wing hit the wall)

*Levo* me je zakačilo (I was hooked on the left)

*Levu* stranu ulice često obilaze ljudi (People often pass by the left side of the street)